50:52.302 --> 51:00.214
You know, they're books, but I realized that there had to be a lot of books in order to,

51:00.937 --> 51:01.698
to study.

51:01.738 --> 51:14.797
So he, we sort of sat, I just sat every day at his feet from 1960 to when I came to come back from Europe to when I left in 80, 90, 65.

51:15.678 --> 51:17.020
Just right wrote down what he said.

51:17.601 --> 51:21.747
It was an unprecedented collaboration between the Tudent and one of the greatest

51:22.013 --> 51:26.661
What's his name again?

