He said, go out to India.

51:41.144 --> 51:44.950
He said, and he told me what to get.

51:45.689 --> 52:06.653
But in the meantime, Gene published a two-volume bibliography of the manuscripts, published kind of semi-positively in Seattle.

52:06.673 --> 52:09.876
I don't know.

52:10.117 --> 52:13.080
Maybe it is.

52:13.904 --> 52:15.806
I'm probably going to work on this this week.

52:16.047 --> 52:28.943
So then the idea was to make them available and some of the European scholars, Tucci was furious that we were going to, he came to see me.

52:29.544 --> 52:30.585
What, in Seattle?

52:30.605 --> 52:32.027
No, in India.

52:32.067 --> 52:33.689
He was allowed into India.

52:33.729 --> 52:36.272
I did, after a long absence.

