But this was in the late 60s.

53:04.734 --> 53:05.274
Yeah.

53:05.334 --> 53:11.721
In the meantime, finally, Gene leaves this out, but in the meantime, he kind of, in a way, bummed around India and Nepal for a couple of years.

53:12.173 --> 53:19.227
And then somehow, I don't know the background here, but somehow a lot of Congress hired him as a local hand.

53:19.247 --> 53:20.008
A local hire.

