54:11.216 --> 54:19.825
In a very positive way, but you're not an antiquarian with respect that you're collecting rarities because they're rare and they're precious.

54:19.925 --> 54:20.766
I'm not interested.

54:20.786 --> 54:22.828
You're looking for content, it seems to me.

