54:24.470 --> 54:29.515
Totally fair, because if you realize the kind of things that could have been bought

54:30.136 --> 54:37.708
for apple and egg in the pond, India, from the Tibetan refugee community in the early 60s that were really treasures.

54:38.910 --> 54:44.158
And why didn't you get the things for the apple and the orange?

54:44.238 --> 54:45.680
It's because I didn't have the apples.

54:47.643 --> 54:53.292
I mean, myself, I grabbed everything I could see, and you would too, I'm sure.

54:53.542 --> 54:56.326
I've already done a few objects, but not so many.

54:57.006 --> 55:00.571
